title: Metallica Quebec Magnetic 2009 BluRay 720p x264 DTS-HD MA 2CH PS
description:
OK, this was a private ReEncode I did for my friends, but results was that good so my friends told me to put this online.

What's good about this release?
this video is ReEncode from original 50GB bluray. what was important to me was audio quality. This release has ORIGINAL DTS-HD Master Audio 2CH Stereo UNTOCHED directly from Bluray. the sound alone is 1.7GB in main video. 

For video quality I also put 5 screenshots from the video so you can check before you download it all.

also what's unique in this release is its subtitle. we gathered all the Lyrics from metallica.com and the rest of speaking also is included too.


Chapters also included.
